race.comment: Tricky race to assess with a few of these at the races for the first time. Of the raced brigade, RUSTENBURG (1) went down by the narrowest of margins on debut before being tipped out for a lengthy spell to furnish. Tuned up for this with a recent trial and a bold showing while fresh would not surprise. STARWARD (8) has had a few chances but has placed two of three over this track and trip and will strip fitter third-up from the spell. Should be right there at the business end. ATOMIC TIME (11) is drawn to get all the favours from the inside alley and may make his presence felt. TRYMESOON (9) next best from the champion Waller yard.
